Now what I want to
do in the next video

00:05:49.090 --> 00:05:52.480
is actually time the car to
figure out how long does it

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.525
take it to do this loop de loop.

00:05:54.525 --> 00:05:56.400
And we're going to assume
that it's a circle.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:57.640
And we're going
to figure it out.

00:05:57.640 --> 00:05:59.223
And we're going to
